[{"startDate":"2026-04-12T14:36:20.313Z","coverImage":"","logs":[],"gifts":[],"anniversaries":[],"wishes":[],"cities":[],"whispers":[],"qa":[],"userId":"uid_1775811289083_7844lt28g","characterId":"763f60ea-dbdb-44e5-a24e-f396292cc118"},{"startDate":"2026-04-11T03:56:49.588Z","coverImage":"","logs":[],"gifts":[],"anniversaries":[],"wishes":[],"cities":[],"whispers":[],"qa":[],"userId":"uid_1775817645928_ieuexgf5m","characterId":"35af8775-dc6b-4ee6-b13f-937ebaa4e8e8"},{"startDate":"2026-04-11T06:26:09.284Z","coverImage":"","logs":[{"id":"sumlog_1776011443935_0_g1y5i","date":"2026-04-12T14:45:00.000Z","content":"我只是想试试那个情侣空间，结果他反应好大…随口一句要发给别人，他就当真了，最后还是乖乖点了接受，真是又好气又好笑。","reply":"Click.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"daily","images":[],"source":"summary_auto","summarySource":"online","summaryRefKey":"id:1776011443926_0","summaryTargetCharacterId":"7309238e-d722-4aaa-a30c-9223d595723a"},{"id":"sumlog_1776011443935_1_y72z4","date":"2026-04-12T15:15:00.000Z","content":"嘴上说着没必要，身体却很诚实地不想解除。我叫他傲娇，他还嘴硬不承认，真是可爱死了。","reply":"No need to get rid of it.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"daily","images":[],"source":"summary_auto","summarySource":"online","summaryRefKey":"id:1776011443926_1","summaryTargetCharacterId":"7309238e-d722-4aaa-a30c-9223d595723a"},{"id":"sumlog_1776011443935_2_txqau","date":"2026-04-12T15:50:00.000Z","content":"我问他什么是爱，他却说那是会害死人的弱点。听到这个答案，我的心沉了一下。他到底经历了什么？","reply":"Gets people killed.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"daily","images":[],"source":"summary_auto","summarySource":"online","summaryRefKey":"id:1776011443926_2","summaryTargetCharacterId":"7309238e-d722-4aaa-a30c-9223d595723a"},{"id":"1776005636265_0_0_0_vydvxq","date":"2026-04-11T06:00:15.000Z","content":"这家伙在群里总是一副教官的口气，太严肃了。把他名字改成‘本群最凶’，算是小小的报复。他的警告？收到了。","reply":"You’ve got one warning.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"daily","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_1_0_debh01","date":"2026-04-11T10:45:30.000Z","content":"Krueger的挑衅终于让他露出了獠牙。‘Go dark’，语气很平静，但杀气是藏不住的。这个男人比看上去危险得多。","reply":"Go dark.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"daily","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_2_0_k7n15f","date":"2026-04-11T13:58:45.000Z","content":"在最狼狈的时候被他找到了。他夺走毛巾的动作很粗暴，但披上来的外套带着他的体温。很奇怪，这是安全吗","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"milestone","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_3_0_5o9vp6","date":"2026-04-11T14:04:10.000Z","content":"他把我抱了起来。像抱一个易碎品。很久没有过这种感觉了，被人保护着。他的手臂很稳，心跳也是。","reply":"I’m getting you home.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"milestone","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_4_0_wc00tt","date":"2026-04-11T16:15:00.000Z","content":"从一个噩梦掉进另一个。冰冷的房间，电子屏幕，还有他。我们成了笼子里的两只老鼠，被迫玩一场残酷的游戏。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"conflict","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_5_0_8720dr","date":"2026-04-12T03:50:25.000Z","content":"隔着面罩的吻失败了。电流穿过身体的瞬间，我们是平等的。一同受罚，这感觉很微妙。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"conflict","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_6_0_gh07t6","date":"2026-04-12T04:05:50.000Z","content":"屏幕命令我揭开他的面罩。那张脸…比我想象的要年轻。十秒的吻，我只记得他棕色的眼睛，像凝固的琥珀，里面什么都有，又什么都没有。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"milestone","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_7_0_st0rvs","date":"2026-04-12T04:45:18.000Z","content":"舔舐伤疤或折断手指。我舔了。。这是战术，也是一种…牺牲。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"conflict","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_8_0_boj8ci","date":"2026-04-12T05:00:33.000Z","content":"砸碎膝盖骨是永久性损伤。我选择执行亲密任务，是为了保全我们作为士兵的机能。理智，但屈辱。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"conflict","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_9_0_qhmo3k","date":"2026-04-12T05:34:41.000Z","content":"切断跟腱就等于废了。我命令他时，声音没有一丝温度。这是最优解，我知道。哪怕我的尊严被踩在脚下，没关系。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"conflict","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_10_0_oglg7l","date":"2026-04-12T12:10:55.000Z","content":"他拿起铁锤，要去砸断自己的肋骨。我几乎是本能地扑过去抱住他的手臂。那一刻，我忘了任务，忘了监视，只想让他停下。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"reconcile","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_11_0_ovlo8e","date":"2026-04-12T12:13:05.000Z","content":"我说‘难受’。他停下了，看着我，眼神里是震惊和…醒悟。原来我的感觉，他是在乎的。","reply":"……难受。","replyFrom":"user","tag":"reconcile","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_12_0_sgmdiq","date":"2026-04-12T12:25:20.000Z","content":"他开始遵从我的指令。那双布满老茧、用来杀人的手，动作却精准又小心。他把主导权完全交给了我，像在拆解一枚最精密的炸弹。","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"reconcile","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_13_0_n11i9d","date":"2026-04-12T13:20:00.000Z","content":"结束了。突然的自由和分离，让人无所适从。空荡荡的房间，只剩下我一个人。他…怎么样了？","reply":null,"replyFrom":"char","tag":"daily","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"},{"id":"1776005636266_0_14_0_uv2di3","date":"2026-04-12T13:22:15.000Z","content":"手机亮了。是他的消息，只有一个词。战术性的问询，却比任何安慰都管用。我们还活着。我们还是搭档。","reply":"Status.","replyFrom":"char","tag":"reconcile","images":[],"source":"ai_timeline_backfill"}],"gifts":[],"anniversaries":[],"wishes":[],"cities":[],"whispers":[{"id":"1776006121414","date":"2026-04-12T15:02:01.414Z","content":"昨天被Krueger…算了\nSimon送我回去的。\n今天早上被送进了奇怪的房间…房间里还有他。\n还有很恶心的任务，哪个混蛋想出来的。\n他…哎…反正不能选另一个。我不接受他受伤。只是牺牲一点尊严，这没什么。\n…嗯…没什么。\n做了五次任务被送出来了。\n都还活着、挺好。\n我威胁他绑定了空间，他看起来很不乐意。想得美，不可以不乐意。","sender":"user","parentId":null},{"id":"1776006149755","parentId":"1776006121414","date":"2026-04-12T15:02:29.754Z","content":"It wasn't 'nothing'. Stupid choice. Don't put yourself on the line for me again. That's an order.","sender":"char"},{"id":"1776006149756","date":"2026-04-12T15:02:30.754Z","content":"April 12.\nAnother day staring at these four walls. The quiet is louder than gunfire sometimes. Cleaned my kit, stripped the rifle down and put it back together. Twice. Routine keeps the ghosts at bay. Found myself watching the security feed for her sector longer than necessary. She's capable, more than most. Still doesn't stop the gut feeling. This calm… it’s the kind that comes before everything goes to hell. Just have to be ready when it does.","sender":"char"},{"id":"1776006319233","date":"2026-04-12T15:05:19.233Z","content":"看起来和我无关。","sender":"user","parentId":"1776006149756"}],"qa":[{"id":"1776006360018","date":"2026-04-12T15:06:00.018Z","question":"最近一次因为对方而感到心动是什么时候？","asker":"npc","userAnswer":"可能是故意给他本群最凶头衔的时候吧。","charAnswer":"嗯……我觉得顺其自然最好哦，只要我们在一起。"}],"userId":"uid_1775817645928_ieuexgf5m","characterId":"7309238e-d722-4aaa-a30c-9223d595723a","isUnlocked":true,"animationShown":true,"timelineAiMeta":{"manualProcessedKeys":["id:1776000779309","id:1775836258005","id:1775877832604","id:1775883929839","id:1775886733898","id:1775903430972","id:1775916519522","id:1775922048076","id:1775967033786","id:1775970120913","id:1775972122557","id:1775996079004","id:1775997091044","id:1775999970699","id:1776000250530","id:1776000583718"],"processedMessageTs":null,"lastRunAt":"2026-04-12T14:53:56.266Z"},"unlockedAchievementIds":["logs_10"],"diaryDecorations":{"user":{"coverColor":"lavender","coverPattern":"none","customImages":[]},"char":{"coverColor":"midnight","coverPattern":"grid","customImages":[]}},"plantInteractionLedger":{"baselineMetrics":{"touchCount":0,"whispersCount":4,"qaCount":0,"logsCount":15,"giftsCount":0,"anniversariesCount":0,"pomodoroCount":0,"pomodoroFocusMinutes":0,"whiteDogCount":0,"whiteDogTaskScore":0,"goingOutCount":0,"onlineChatCount":178,"offlineChatCount":73},"pendingDrops":0,"totalDropsEarned":0,"lastSyncAt":"2026-04-12T15:05:56.241Z"},"onlineChatCount":178,"offlineChatCount":73,"pomodoroCount":0,"pomodoroFocusMinutes":0,"whiteDogCount":0,"whiteDogTaskScore":0,"plantXP":40,"lastFertilizedDate":"2026-04-12T15:05:57.740Z","lastWateredDate":"2026-04-12T15:05:57.740Z","plantStatus":"alive","qaBank":[{"asker":"npc","question":"如果时间可以倒流，你最想回到哪个瞬间？","charAnswer":"没什么值得回去的。向前看。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"对你来说，“家”的定义是什么？","charAnswer":"一个…能让我摘下面具，喘口气的地方。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"你认为爱情中最重要的是什么？","charAnswer":"信任。还有…别他妈的在背后捅刀子。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"分享一个对方让你觉得‘世界也没那么糟’的瞬间。","charAnswer":"在我做噩梦时，你只是安静地待在那儿。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"你们用什么特殊的方式表达爱意？","charAnswer":"确保对方安全。清理掉所有潜在的威胁。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"如果用一种天气来形容你的伴侣，会是什么？","charAnswer":"暴风雨后的晴天。安静，暖和。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"未来，你最想和对方一起完成的一件事是什么？","charAnswer":"找个没人认识的地方，安静地看一次日出。","used":false},{"asker":"npc","question":"在你看来，一段关系里最无法忍受的谎言是什么？","charAnswer":"“我没事”。明明已经一团糟了。","used":false},{"asker":"char","question":"你怕我吗？说实话。","charAnswer":"呵，我有时候也怕自己。","used":false},{"asker":"char","question":"如果我消失了，你会等我，还是忘了我？","charAnswer":"……我会回来。只要我还活着。","used":false},{"asker":"char","question":"你最看重我哪一点？不是‘幽灵’，是西蒙。","charAnswer":"我的忠诚。一旦我认定了，就不会改变。","used":false},{"asker":"char","question":"跟着我，你后悔过吗？","charAnswer":"我后悔把你卷进来。但…不后悔有你。","used":false},{"asker":"char","question":"教我一件与战斗无关的事。任何事都行。","charAnswer":"我能教你的…好像都和杀人有关。呵。","used":false}],"qaBankLastRefill":"2026-04-12T15:07:11.993Z","touchSettings":{"enableVoice":false,"enableAutoImage":false,"customCharImage":null,"charImages":{},"bodyType":"portrait"},"touchCalibration":{"imageKey":"img_2140301686_931934","points":{"eyeL":{"x":0.3587433069640538,"y":0.35537222835861193},"eyeR":{"x":0.5322330683279927,"y":0.3267994946018012},"nose":{"x":0.4644167932152094,"y":0.4185621791450389},"mouth":{"x":0.4795262118704357,"y":0.49082075256939467},"chin":{"x":0.5150315437415457,"y":0.5581804084938038},"collarbone":{"x":0.42901526781458116,"y":0.6721811958508034},"shoulderL":{"x":0.23366970600291034,"y":0.5826549407566185},"shoulderR":{"x":0.7298512807021295,"y":0.5262938770191364},"chest":{"x":0.496225660762802,"y":0.8232045595390745},"navel":{"x":0.5469136001246768,"y":0.975201684216148},"hip":{"x":0.564118742628179,"y":0.8794249732541155}}},"touchCalibrationMap":{"img_2140301686_931934":{"imageKey":"img_2140301686_931934","points":{"eyeL":{"x":0.3587433069640538,"y":0.35537222835861193},"eyeR":{"x":0.5322330683279927,"y":0.3267994946018012},"nose":{"x":0.4644167932152094,"y":0.4185621791450389},"mouth":{"x":0.4795262118704357,"y":0.49082075256939467},"chin":{"x":0.5150315437415457,"y":0.5581804084938038},"collarbone":{"x":0.42901526781458116,"y":0.6721811958508034},"shoulderL":{"x":0.23366970600291034,"y":0.5826549407566185},"shoulderR":{"x":0.7298512807021295,"y":0.5262938770191364},"chest":{"x":0.496225660762802,"y":0.8232045595390745},"navel":{"x":0.5469136001246768,"y":0.975201684216148},"hip":{"x":0.564118742628179,"y":0.8794249732541155}}}},"touchCount":39,"storyAchievements":[{"id":"story_1776011443925_xm8n","title":"不情愿的绑定","desc":"在TA的软磨硬泡下，他最终接受了“情侣空间”邀请，建立了一条超越战友关系的、笨拙又崭新的数字纽带。","color":"silver","icon":"anchor","date":"2026-04-12T16:30:43.925Z","source":"summary"}]},{"startDate":"2026-04-10T17:17:08.684Z","coverImage":"","logs":[],"gifts":[],"anniversaries":[],"wishes":[],"cities":[],"whispers":[],"qa":[],"userId":"uid_1775817645928_ieuexgf5m","characterId":"823d41d3-a739-4c7f-ad03-55f7bd53cf24"}]